description:
Fine Cooking - Cook Fresh - 150 Recipes for Cooking and Eating Fresh Year-Round (2013).pdf Gooner

Publisher: Taunton Press (February 5, 2013)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1600859593
ISBN-13: 978-1600859595

Although there continues to be a growing emphasis on eating healthfully, cooks want to make food that is not only good for them but delicious and satisfying as well. At "Fine Cooking," this approach is based on using the best, freshest, locally grown fruits and vegetables you can find as well as the most sustainable meats, poultry, and seafood you can get your hands on. This recipe-packed guide to cooking and eating fresh features 150 delicious recipes for seasonal eating year-round. Handy sidebars and food profiles help home cooks choose, prep, and use seasonal produce, meats, and seafood so they can shop smarter and eat better
